-------------Fluxbox configuration

Author: Reuben Joseph <rejnex@gmail.com>
Version: 1.0

Here are some applications that I think fit with 
fluxbox's minimilistic philosophy

-------------Suggested apps for fluxbox
feh             :lighweight image viewer and wallpapers setter
conky           :Everyone's favorite system monitor
rox-filer       :lightweight file manager
htop            :better looking top replacement
xterm/uxterm    :default terminal emulator urxvt is another alternative
dmenu           :minimalistic application launcher
mutt            :curses based mail client (takes some time to configure)
mpd             :The music player daemon
sonata          :gtk+ based frontend to MPD




